Class LCG64ShiftRandom.Param

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jenetics.util.LCG64ShiftRandom.Param
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    LCG64ShiftRandom

    public static final class LCG64ShiftRandom.Param
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Parameter class for the LCG64ShiftRandom generator, for the parameters a and b of the LC recursion ri+1 = a · ri + b mod 264.
    Since:
    1.1
    Version:
    2.0
